EIP_712-and ECDSA with Frontend

1.First deploy  Mytoken contract with permit function
2.Deploy permit.js script . It will log all the required details which can be used in permit function in smart contract

set the path cd to index.html before deploying frontend
Can use frontend to do the whole process in one place 

ECDSA
Deploy Erc20ForEcdsa.sol
1.Then deployEcdsa.js which will send deployed Erc20 Ecdsa tokens and hold some tokens
2.Provide reciever and amount to deployEcdsa.js and it will return a signature 
3.The reciever can use the signature to claim the tokens from Erc20 ECDSA contract by triggering claim token

